
#NOTES

## Namming and convetions

	* **geometry** - a 4 element array containing the positions and size of a window acording on screen size.
		  Each array element can the size of the window in pixels or an simple algebric
		  expression.

	* **numeric geometry** - a geometry with absolute values only. I.e. only numbers, no
				algebric expression

	* **arrangement** - an array of geometries representing the position and size of multple windows.

